OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly dry
OL,6,Fevening and night across the region
OL,7,Fwith some clear intervals developing,
OL,8,Fespecially towards the north. Staying
OL,9,Fhumid allowing some mist and low cloud
OL,10,Fto form.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA grey and potentially murky
OL,13,Fstart, however cloud will gradually
OL,14,Fthin and break allowing skies to
OL,15,Fbrighten. Some sunny spells developing
OL,16,Fduring the afternoon, especially in
OL,17,Fthe southeast. Feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
