OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry on Friday with bright spells.
OL,7,FOtherwise lots of fine weather on the
OL,8,Fweekend, with lots of sunshine. Very
OL,9,Fwarm by day, with nights also staying
OL,10,Fwarm and humid.
